results.story: The Comme des Garçons Play x Converse Chuck 70 High ‘Pristine Red’ updates the heritage silhouette with ultra-colorful tooling. The upper is constructed from cream-colored canvas with a tonal rubber toe cap and a contrasting black webbing heel strip. CDG Play’s iconic heart-and-eyes logo peers out from the lateral ankle, while a traditional All Star patch adorns the opposite side. The high-top rides on a crimson rubber midsole, featuring the Chuck 70’s signature glossy sidewalls and white pinstripe detailing.

results.name: Converse Chuck Taylor All-Star 70 Ox Comme des Garcons PLAY Egret Red Midsole
results.story: The Comme des Garçons Play x Converse Chuck 70 Low ‘Pristine Red’ gives the heritage silhouette a bold new design, highlighted by a solid crimson midsole — a first in the collaborative series that began in 2009. The eye-catching hue is applied to the Chuck 70’s signature glossy sidewalls, accented with off-white pinstripe detailing and a Converse All Star license plate. The upper is built with cream-colored canvas and features CDG Play’s signature eyes-and-heart logo on the lateral side.

results.name: Converse Chuck Taylor All-Star 70 Ox Comme des Garcons PLAY Black Red Midsole
results.story: The Comme des Garçons Play x Converse Chuck 70 Low ‘Black Red’ makes over the classic silhouette with a red rubber midsole, featuring glossy sidewalls and black pinstripe detailing. A tonal Converse All Star license plate decorates the heel. The upper is constructed from black canvas with contrast white stitching and a reinforced rubber toe cap. Designed by graphic artist Filip Pagowski, CDG Play’s signature heart-and-eyes logo is stamped on the lateral side.

results.name: Converse Chuck Taylor All-Star 70 Hi Comme des Garcons PLAY Black Red Midsole
results.story: The Comme des Garçons Play x Converse Chuck 70 High ‘Black Red’ debuts a bold crimson finish on the glossy rubber midsole — a first in a creative partnership that dates back to 2009. Up top, the black canvas build is accented with a white webbing heel strip and CDG Play’s heart-and-eyes logo. Traditional Chuck details remain intact, including a reinforced white rubber toe cap, winged stitching atop the tongue, and a circular All Star patch on the medial ankle.

Converse Chuck Taylor All-Star Flyease Egret String
results.story: The Chuck Taylor All Star CX FlyEase ‘Egret Light Silver’ treats the foundational sneaker to a comprehensive design overhaul centered around Nike’s groundbreaking FlyEase technology. The low-top utilizes an off-white stretch canvas upper with a restructured heel that collapses and springs back, allowing for hands-free on and off. A green-tinged translucent cage wraps around the back of the midsole, revealing lightweight CX foam cushioning. Underfoot, an outsole pattern inspired by the original Chuck Taylor delivers reliable traction.

results.name: Converse Chuck Taylor All-Star Flyease Black Wild Mango
results.story: The Converse Chuck Taylor All Star CX FlyEase ‘Black Wild Mango’ brings Nike’s groundbreaking easy-entry technology to the sneaker icon. Black stretch canvas is utilized on the upper, featuring traditional lace closure and an innovative TPE heel cage that’s designed to flex and collapse, allowing wearers to step into the shoe hands-free. The heel then rebounds, locking the foot in place. The sneaker rides on a bright orange CX foam midsole, made visible through a wraparound translucent heel cage.

results.name: Converse Chuck Taylor All-Star Flyease White Wild Mango
results.story: The Converse Chuck Taylor All Star CX FlyEase ‘White Wild Mango’ overhauls the foundational sneaker with Nike’s revolutionary easy access technology. Constructed from stretch white canvas, the streamlined upper features a padded low-cut collar and a TPE heel cage that flexes, collapses, and rebounds, enabling hands-free on and off. Lightweight cushioning is provided by an orange CX foam midsole, exposed through a translucent cage that wraps around the heel.

results.name: Converse Weapon CX Joshua Vides Black Clear
results.story: The Joshua Vides x Converse Weapon CX ‘Made in Studio’ is taken from a capsule collection with the LA-based artist. Inspired by craftsmanship and process, this reworked Weapon features a black organic canvas upper with frayed edges and transparent TPU on the quarter panel and toe box. Dual Converse and Joshua Vides branding appears on the woven tongue tag and genuine cork insole. The sneaker rides on an exaggerated midsole built with injected EVA, good for lightweight cushioning with each step.

results.name: Converse Pro Leather Joshua Vides Natural Ivory
results.story: The Joshua Vides x Converse Pro Leather ‘Made in Studio’ presents the visual artist’s modern interpretation of a hardwood classic. The unique build is intended to tell the story of craftsmanship and process, highlighted by an off-white organic canvas upper secured with measuring tape laces. Digitally printed black lines resemble imperfect marker strokes, while durable TecTuff leather at the toe and heel mimics the look of black duct tape. Dual Converse and Joshua Vides branding appears on the woven tongue tag and cork insole.

results.name: Converse Chuck Taylor All-Star 70 Hi Joshua Vides White
results.story: Launching as part of a capsule collection with the LA-based artist, the Joshua Vides x Converse Chuck 70 High ‘Made in Studio’ transforms the sneaker icon with a revamped design that honors artistic craftsmanship. A zip-up shroud composed of white Tyvek material envelops the upper, built with black organic canvas and embellished with 3D-printed white polka dots. Black tumbled leather is utilized on the tongue and a pull tab at the heel. The high-top is mounted on an off-white rubber midsole, accented with black pinstripes and supported by a translucent rubber outsole.

results.name: Converse Chuck Taylor All-Star 70 Ox Golf Wang Python Blue
results.story: The Golf Wang x Converse Chuck Taylor 1970 Low ‘Blue Python’ showcases Tyler, the Creator’s love of eye-catching prints and luxe fashion. The iconic silhouette replaces traditional canvas construction with snakeskin-embossed leather in Blue Topaz. The pastel hue is repeated on the translucent rubber midsole, accented with a Converse license plate at the heel and supported by a matching blue diamond-traction rubber outsole. Converse and Golf Want branding appears atop a cushioned Ortholite insole.

results.name: Converse Chuck Taylor All-Star 70 Ox Golf Wang Python Pink
results.story: The Golf Wang x Converse Chuck Taylor 1970 Low ‘Pink Python’ delivers Tyler, the Creator’s exotic take on the foundational sneaker. Instead of traditional canvas, the upper is built with snakeskin-embossed leather in a pastel pink finish. Details include a tonal rubber toe cap, chrome eyelets, and winged tongue stitching. Dual Converse and Golf Wang branding is stamped on the Ortholite sockliner. Anchoring the low-top is a pink-tinged translucent rubber midsole and outsole.

results.name: Converse CONS One Star Pro Carhartt WIP
results.story: The Carhartt WIP x Converse One Star Pro Cons Low ‘White Black’ reimagines the vintage hoops shoe as a skate-ready low-top. Neutral off-white tones are executed on a paneled upper built with a blend of canvas, suede and leather. A die-cut One Star logo adorns the quarter panel, while dual CONS and Carhartt branding is stamped on the cushioned CX Foam insole. The minimalist silhouette sits atop a black rubber midsole with a gum rubber toe bumper for added durability.

results.name: Converse CONS Fastbreak Pro Carhartt WIP
results.story: The Carhartt WIP x Converse Fastbreak Pro Cons Mid ‘White Black’ delivers a skate-ready take on a retro basketball shoe originally released in 1983. The mid-top sports a mixed-material build, highlighted by canvas, leather and suede paneling in beige and off-white tones. Star Chevron branding decorates the quarter panel, while the tongue tag displays a hybrid Carhartt/CONS logo. Inside the shoe, a CX foam sockliner provides lightweight cushioning with each step. A gum rubber outsole yields grippy traction underfoot.

results.story: The Rick Owens x Converse Chuck 70 Low DRKSTAR ‘Black’ delivers the designer’s third collaboration with the iconic sportswear brand. Releasing alongside an accompanying high-top, this Ox version features an upper built with black 18oz cotton twill. Details include contrast white stitching, a rounded rubber toe cap, and an elongated tongue, accented with an oversized TURBODRK tag. The sneaker is mounted on a distorted rubber midsole, featuring black pinstripe detailing and reinforced overlays that wrap around the forefoot and heel.

results.name: Converse DRKSTAR Chuck Taylor All-Star 70 Hi Rick Owens DRKSHDW White
results.story: The Rick Owens x Converse Chuck 70 High DRKSTAR ‘Lily White’ reunites the influential fashion designer with the American sportswear brand for a third go-round. Twinned with an accompanying low-top, this pair features a white cotton twill upper with chrome eyelets and a rounded rubber toe cap. Branding elements include an All Star patch on the medial ankle and a woven DRKSTAR tag on an elongated tongue. The sneaker’s rubber midsole is updated with segmented sidewalls, while a standard Chuck 70 outsole delivers grippy traction underfoot.

results.name: Converse Chuck Taylor All-Star 70 Hi thisisneverthat Lemon Icing
results.story: The thisisneverthat x Converse Chuck 70 High ‘New Vintage’ delivers the Korean streetwear brand’s unique take on the sneaker icon. The upper is constructed from tan hairy suede and accented with a circular All Star patch on the medial ankle. A pre-yellowed finish is applied to the rubber toe cap and midsole, featuring contrasting black pinstripes and mismatched license plates marked with Converse and thisisneverthat branding. A turquoise rubber outsole offers grippy traction underfoot.

results.name: Converse One Star thisisneverthat Poseidon

Details include a black One Star logo, chrome eyelets and a dual-branded woven tongue tag. The low-top is mounted on a distressed black rubber midsole with throwback embossed-star detailing on the toe bumper. Underfoot, a turquoise rubber outsole delivers an unexpected pop of color.

Borrowed from one of Basquiat’s iconic oil paintings, a multicolor abstract print enlivens a low-profile upper built with black poly canvas. Each tongue tag is embellished with Converse and Basquiat branding, a mismatched motif that’s repeated on the license plates that decorate the sneaker’s off-white rubber midsoles.

The design adds color to a black poly canvas upper with tonal suede overlays and a blacked-out All Star patch on the medial ankle. The high-top is mounted on a white rubber midsole, featuring black pinstripes and mismatched Converse and Basquiat branding on each license plate.

results.story: The Rick Owens x Converse TURBOWPN Mid ‘Black Cloud Cream’ delivers the fashion designer’s modern interpretation of an ‘80s hardwood mainstay, the Converse Weapon. The blacked-out upper is constructed from premium tumbled leather and accented with stylized one-star iconography on the lateral quarter panel. An oversized woven label atop the elongated tongue displays dual Converse and DRKSHDW branding. The sneaker rides on a pre-yellowed platform midsole, supported underfoot by a solid black rubber outsole. A drop-in CX foam insole provides lightweight cushioning with each step.

results.name: Converse Jack Purcell Moncler Fragment Black
results.story: Launching as part of a collaborative three-piece pack designed by Hiroshi Fujiwara, the Fragment Design x Moncler x Converse Jack Purcell ‘Black’ makes use of a 12oz canvas upper with contrast white stitching. The reinforced rubber toe cap is etched with the signature Jack Purcell ‘smile,’ while the dual-branded heel strip displays Moncler’s ‘M’ logo and Fragment’s lightning bolt emblem. The low-top is mounted on a white rubber midsole, featuring ‘Moncler/Fragment’ printed in block lettering across the lateral sidewall.

results.name: Converse Chuck Taylor All-Star 70s Hi Comme des Garcons PLAY Grey
results.story: The Comme des Garçons PLAY x Converse Chuck 70 High ‘Steel Gray’ highlights neutral tones on Rei Kawakubo’s reimagined Chuck. The grey canvas upper is decorated on the lateral side with an oversized heart and eyes logo in simple black and white. The icon is repeated in red atop the dual-branded Ortholite sockliner, good for lightweight cushioning with each step. The high-top is mounted on an Egret-colored rubber midsole, reinforced underfoot by a diamond-traction rubber outsole in a traditional brown finish.

results.name: Converse Chuck Taylor All-Star 70 Hi Comme des Garcons PLAY Blue
results.story: The Comme des Garçons PLAY x Converse Chuck 70 High ‘Blue Quartz’ features a traditional canvas build dominated by Filip Pagowski’s instantly familiar heart and eyes logo. On the sneaker’s lateral side, the oversized icon stands out in black and white against a royal blue backdrop. Traditional Chuck 70 components are present and accounted for, including contrast stitching, chrome eyelets, a reinforced rubber toe cap and a circular All Star patch on the medial ankle. Lightweight cushioning is provided by an Ortholite sockliner, featuring dual Converse and CDG Play branding.

results.name: Converse Chuck Taylor All-Star 70 Ox Comme des Garcons PLAY Grey
results.story: The Comme des Garçons PLAY x Converse Chuck 70 Low ‘Steel Gray’ showcases the Japanese brand’s iconic heart and eyes logo in a simple black and white finish. The oversized icon is cropped on the lateral side of the upper, constructed from sturdy grey canvas with contrast stitching and a reinforced rubber toe cap. Dual Converse and CDG Play branding is stamped on the Ortholite insole. The low-top is mounted on an off-white rubber midsole, featuring the Chuck 70’s signature raised sidewalls and a tonal license plate at the heel.
